Here we have **3 Rows** and **3 Columns**

Also notice how the width of different rows and columns are different.

Add the below **Grid properties** to the css

```css
.bg-container {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: 1fr 3fr 1fr;
  gap: 15px;
}
```

